MonitoringLocationDescriptionText: 05/28/2012    Sampling site is located in forest area in Mount Nebo State Wildlife Management Area.  Bank-to-bank width:  3  meters; Bank height:  2 meter; Midstream depth (at site): about 25 cm.  Vegetation adjacent site: maple, cherry, oak, fern  Watershed land use:  forest and wetlands, roads and some residential use  Upstream disturbance:  roads and residential use    Tag number:  458. Tag tree description:  30 cm DBH maple on right bank, looking upstream.  Note:  In 2013, tag tree was uprooted and fallen down, but tag was still attached.
